Package: scRepertoire
Title: A toolkit for single-cell immune receptor profiling
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Nick",
           family = "Borcherding",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "ncborch@gmail.com")
Description: scRepertoire was built to process data derived from the 10x Genomics Chromium Immune Profiling for both T-cell receptor (TCR) and immunoglobulin (Ig) enrichment workflows and subsequently interacts with the popular Seurat R package.
